CONTROLLED MOVEMENT:

		forward   ----->'f','distance in mm'
		backward  ----->'b','distance in mm'
		turn left ----->'l','angle in degree'
		turn right----->'r','angle in degree'
		stop  --------->'s'

UNCONTROLLED MOVEMENT:

		forward    ----->'w'
		backward   ----->'z'
		left turn  ----->'a'
		right turn ----->'d'
		stop   --------->'s'

TURN SERVO:

		head ------>'h','angle'
		base ------>'g','angle'
